# Deploy payload allow-list by exclusion: only build-relevant files go up.
# Without this file the CLI was shipping ~45MB of local junk (audit reports,
# outreach state) on every deploy, and prospect data must never leave the box.

# local state + reports (gitignored locally, but the CLI uploads them anyway)
docs/audit
.lighthouseci
data
_assets-archive
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# outreach + email ops: local-only, contain prospect contact details
scripts/outreach
scripts/send-*.mjs
scripts/schedule-*.mjs
scripts/cancel-*.mjs
docs/email-auth
docs/email-send-safety.md
infra

# workspace notes, not site source
00_INBOX
POSITIONING.md
LAUNCH_HANDOFF.md
BRIEF.md
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
.claude
.hermes
